Brunch at @pog_dublin 
What we had:
Kinder Bueno protein pancakes (very very filling)
Breakfast brioche (without bacon of course!)
Banana Bread (this was the star of the show!)
:
@pog_dublin is also serving their seasonal summer drinks:
Iced Matcha with strawberry cold foam
Watermelon spritz (asked for it to be non alcoholic)
Pistachio affogato (such a great combination 🤎💚☕️)
:
Absolutely enjoyed this and would definitely go back for the banana bread!
